users can track progress of task using the status boxes on the scheduled tasks or the progress boxes next to the task
yearly planner offers stickys these are plaed on events or tasks that have been created that occur on the same date every year, user can also include stickers on these eg balloons for bday

monthly planner offers "repeats" these can be set to any task to repeat into the next month
day schedule, choose a start time from the drop down of times create task first task begins at the start time set duration of task, automatic break from tasks after 12 and 3 and 6 etc depending on how many tasks set throughout the day , set status of task to see how many you have
The day planner starts with a pop of either creating a schedule or just a simple task when adding new task drop down of days works the same for monthly and yearly
Tasks are structed and listed according to priority users will be asked to set a priority for a task and based on this and the due dates, the most urgent tasks appear at the top....
Creating a task users can choose to be reminded of the task and based on how questions were answered on sign up is how often user will be reminded of that task
